{"tid":1327834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FF討論]2047年前後香港會變成點?","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:58:53.000Z","uid":157522,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af372fdcbb86138a0e3051c71ed5a626a4953930","tid":1327834,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"我近排有幾個迷思好想大家一齊FF下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">衣食住行</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>2047年後港幣繼續流通?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>仲可唔可以自由地上Youtube/FB/IG?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>言論自由一定無，最起碼一定會受限制<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>丁權被沒收，大量原居民抗爭引發暴動，但被長居香港多年嘅新移民反對下交出丁權<br />\n(大家都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>回歸40左右會有民主，香港人每人一票選特首，但只有一人可以選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>50年內來港嘅150人單程證已佔香港人口70%，有民主都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>近40年每人來港嘅150人單程證會繼續留係香港定已經搬民哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>回歸45年左右，樓市恐慌性拋售，一年內爆破<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">結局</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>2047年後香港永久變成特別行政區<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>2047年後香港繼續實行一國兩制(不過係名存實亡)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>2047年後香港正式回歸，但港幣/行政/立法繼續保持不變<br />\n<del><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">* </span></strong>中央覺得香港太麻煩，直接放棄香港(最好啦)</del>"},{"pid":"898a226e3bee7cba40992ccf7f58848705650876","tid":1327834,"uid":2508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"2047香港已經獨立左，講完"},{"pid":"dfa80119cdc7a8f2433e20a4f31f22d484d96699","tid":1327834,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"廢除港幣，統一人民幣"},{"pid":"3945a18b8fd4283a96395454a6991b4230f3405b","tid":1327834,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"898a226e3bee7cba40992ccf7f58848705650876","tid":1327834,"uid":2508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"2047香港已經獨立左，講完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"香港比中共揸住個春袋呀<br />\n毒條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港只係試刀<br />\n台灣先係中共主菜呀<br />\n<br />\n原本計劃想每日150個淡化香港<br />\n依家最希望中国人當香港跳板<br />\n2046年走撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 好灰呀<br />\n大家721呀屌"},{"pid":"98985331633e9f3f8dfab08b3aab55475b1fbec7","tid":1327834,"uid":190573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"淨係一堆2047到期嘅地契已經足以令香港人暴動<br />\n不過到咗2047外國已經幫唔到香港，因為一國兩制已經到期，就算香港變成新疆，外國最多都係出聲話表示關注，咩都唔會做到"},{"pid":"d51030bf77575c5866752a6525d8c1ee905632ad","tid":1327834,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98985331633e9f3f8dfab08b3aab55475b1fbec7","tid":1327834,"uid":190573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"淨係一堆2047到期嘅地契已經足以令香港人暴動<br />\n不過到咗2047外國已經幫唔到香港，因為一國兩制已經到期，就算香港變成新疆，外國最多都係出聲話表示關注，咩都唔會做到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:00:59.000Z","msg":"真係同班仆街鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03df713826ffefb3d4e93edcbbf6df73faa95efe","tid"